FIND PARTS BY MACHINE TYPE

Robomow original equipment parts can help you maintain your Robomow outdoor power equipment long-term. Find parts by machine type: Riding Lawn Mower, Walk Behind Lawn Mower, Garden Tiller and Snow Blower to repair your machine.

RX20

The Robomow RX robotic lawn mower is ideal for small lawns up to 1/20 acre (200sq.m). Contained within the lawn by installing a perimeter wire, the compact mower leaves its charging station once a day to cut the grass before returning to the base to recharge. With a maximum cut height of 1.75", the Robomow RX20 maintains that fresh, always-mowed look for the small, urban lawn!

SHOP RX20
RC306

The Robomow RC306 robotic lawn mower is perfect for medium-sized lawns of up to 1/8 acre. The battery-powered mower is app-controlled, leaving its base station to cut the grass as directed by its owner. Equipped with a rain sensor and anti-theft system, the Robomow RC306 keeps medium-sized lawns perfectly cut and edged all season long.

SHOP RC306
RS612

The Robomow RS612 robotic lawn mower can easily cut larger lawns up to 3/4 acre with a uniquely powerful cutting system and multi-zone capabilities. The RS mows automatically and easily managed via the app, returning to charge after each mow. TurboMow feature allows for cutting even high grass with ease, keeping larger lawns manicured without the hassle.

SHOP RS612
